---
// V5 parity (Phase 5.1) — bloc B2B "Simplifiez vos achats" 2 colonnes :
//   - Gauche : pitch + 3 bénéfices + 2 CTA (Créer compte pro, Demander devis)
//   - Droite : carte blanche avec mini-formulaire devis pré-rempli
//
// Le formulaire pointe vers /devis avec les champs déjà visibles, pour
// réduire la friction. La submit redirige vers /devis qui contient le
// vrai endpoint (ré-utilise la logique anti-bot honeypot existante).
---

<section class="border-t border-primary/5 bg-bg-soft py-14" aria-label="Service professionnels">
  <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-10 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-16 lg:px-8">
    <div>
      <span class="label-category">Professionnels</span>
      <h2 class="mt-3 font-display text-3xl font-semibold leading-tight text-primary sm:text-4xl">
        Simplifiez vos achats,<br />multipliez vos avantages.
      </h2>
      <ul class="mt-8 space-y-4 text-sm text-primary/80">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span
            class="mt-0.5 flex h-7 w-7 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary"
            aria-hidden="true"
          >
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              width="14"
              height="14"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
            >
              <rect width="20" height="14" x="2" y="5" rx="2"></rect>
              <path d="M2 10h20"></path>
            </svg>
          </span>
          <span>Conditions de paiement personnalisées et facturation à 30 jours fin de mois.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span
            class="mt-0.5 flex h-7 w-7 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary"
            aria-hidden="true"
          >
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              width="14"
              height="14"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
            >
              <path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path>
              <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle>
              <path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path>
              <path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"></path>
            </svg>
          </span>
          <span>Gestion multi-comptes et centres de coûts pour les grandes structures.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span
            class="mt-0.5 flex h-7 w-7 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary"
            aria-hidden="true"
          >
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              width="14"
              height="14"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
            >
              <path d="M19 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H9a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path>
              <circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"></circle>
            </svg>
          </span>
          <span>Interlocuteur unique dédié pour vos besoins spécifiques et volume.</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4">
        <a
          href="/inscription?type=pro"
          class="inline-flex h-11 items-center gap-2 rounded-btn bg-accent px-5 text-sm font-semibold text-primary transition-colors hover:bg-accent-hover"
        >
          Créer mon compte Pro
          <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/devis" class="text-sm font-medium text-primary underline-offset-4 hover:underline">
          Demander un devis
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <form
      method="get"
      action="/devis"
      class="rounded-card border border-primary/10 bg-white p-6 shadow-card sm:p-8"
    >
      <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-primary">Devis gratuit en 1 heure</h3>
      <div class="mt-6 grid gap-4">
        <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
          <label class="block">
            <span class="label-category text-primary/60">Société</span>
            <input
              type="text"
              name="company_name"
              autocomplete="organization"
              placeholder="Nom de l'entreprise"
              class="mt-1 h-10 w-full rounded-btn border border-primary/15 bg-bg-soft px-3 text-sm text-primary placeholder:text-primary/40 focus:border-accent focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-accent/30"
            />
          </label>
          <label class="block">
            <span class="label-category text-primary/60">SIRET</span>
            <input
              type="text"
              name="siret"
              inputmode="numeric"
              pattern="[0-9]{14}"
              placeholder="14 chiffres"
              class="mt-1 h-10 w-full rounded-btn border border-primary/15 bg-bg-soft px-3 text-sm text-primary placeholder:text-primary/40 focus:border-accent focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-accent/30"
            />
          </label>
        </div>
        <label class="block">
          <span class="label-category text-primary/60">Email professionnel</span>
          <input
            type="email"
            name="email"
            autocomplete="email"
            placeholder="contact@entreprise.fr"
            class="mt-1 h-10 w-full rounded-btn border border-primary/15 bg-bg-soft px-3 text-sm text-primary placeholder:text-primary/40 focus:border-accent focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-accent/30"
          />
        </label>
        <label class="block">
          <span class="label-category text-primary/60">Votre projet</span>
          <textarea
            name="message"
            rows="3"
            placeholder="Décrivez brièvement vos besoins…"
            class="mt-1 w-full rounded-btn border border-primary/15 bg-bg-soft px-3 py-2 text-sm text-primary placeholder:text-primary/40 focus:border-accent focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-accent/30"
          ></textarea>
        </label>
        <button
          type="submit"
          class="inline-flex h-11 items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-btn bg-accent text-sm font-semibold text-primary transition-colors hover:bg-accent-hover"
        >
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            width="16"
            height="16"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            aria-hidden="true"
          >
            <path d="m22 2-7 20-4-9-9-4Z"></path>
            <path d="M22 2 11 13"></path>
          </svg>
          Envoyer la demande
        </button>
      </div>
    </form>
  </div>
</section>
